<style 
      xmlns="http://purl.org/net/xbiblio/csl"
      class="note"
      version="1.0">
  <info>
    <id />
    <title />
    <updated>2009-08-10T04:49:00+09:00</updated>
  </info>
  <locale>
    <terms>
      <term form="short" name="Chapter">ch.</term>
      <term form="short" name="Section">sec.</term>
      <term form="short" name="chapter">ch.</term>
      <term form="symbol" name="chapter">ch.</term>
      <term form="symbol" name="page"></term>
    </terms>
  </locale>
  <macro name="locator">
    <group delimiter=" ">
      <choose>
        <if locator="page" match="none">
          <label form="symbol" variable="locator"/>
        </if>
      </choose>
      <number label-form="symbol" variable="locator"/>
    </group>
  </macro>
  <macro name="citation">
      <group delimiter=" ">
        <text variable="title"/>
        <group is-parallel="true">
           <text value="[PARALLEL]"/>
        </group>
        <text variable="container-title"/>
        <date variable="original-date" form="text" date-parts="year" prefix="(" suffix=")"/>
      </group>
  </macro>
  <citation>
    <layout delimiter=", ">
      <choose>
        <if position="subsequent">
          <text macro="citation"/>
        </if>
        <else>
          <text macro="citation"/>
        </else>
      </choose>
    </layout>
  </citation>
</style>
